short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Initiate phone calls from any website with TalentLynk Click-to-Call

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: TalentLynk's Click-to-Call extension allows you to start a phone call from any website that has phone number links present. It integrates especially well with the Bullhorn Vincere and Loxo CRMs.
